These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, soy-milk, water, 7up
Game: bridge, scrabble, poker, canasta
1. Game:scrabble is on the left of Game:bridge##1
2. Beverage:mirinda == Game:canasta##1
3. Game:poker is on the right of Game:bridge##1
4. Beverage:soy-milk is on the left of Game:canasta##1
5. Beverage:7up is on the left of Game:bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | 7up | water | soy-milk | mirinda   |
| Game   | scrabble  | bridge     | poker   | canasta |

