.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Flower: zinnia, dahlia, iris, daffodil
Movie-Genre: scientific, satire, western, disaster
1. Flower:daffodil == Movie-Genre:satire##1
2. Flower:zinnia is on the far right##1
3. Flower:dahlia is on the right of Flower:daffodil##1
4. Flower:daffodil is on the right of Movie-Genre:western##1
5. Movie-Genre:satire is on the left of Movie-Genre:scientific##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Flower   | iris | daffodil | dahlia | zinnia    |
| Movie-Genre   | western    | satire      | scientific | disaster |

